    <item>
      <title>全球 IT 中断影响了英国各地的医生预约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-outage-is-hitting-doctor-appointments-across-the-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国各地的医生就诊受到了全球计算机中断的影响，人们担心这种情况会给患者带来风险，并给本已陷入困境的国家医疗服务体系带来进一步的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-outage-is-hitting-doctor-appointments-across-the-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:21:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 首席执行官表示已部署修复全球中断的措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-ceo-says-fix-for-global-outage-has-been-deployed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 的首席执行官表示，公司已经确定了导致全球 Windows 系统崩溃的更新，并且“已经部署了修复程序”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-ceo-says-fix-for-global-outage-has-been-deployed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:07:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球 IT 中断影响纽约早晨通勤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-outage-to-hit-new-york-dc-morning-commutes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此次技术故障导致全球航空公司、银行和交易所普遍中断，预计将于周五影响美国早间通勤，纽约地铁在 X 上的一篇帖子中表示，大部分线路的到站信息无法提供。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-outage-to-hit-new-york-dc-morning-commutes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:03:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国准备使用干扰设备攻击俄罗斯和中国卫星</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/us-space-force-prepares-jammers-to-blunt-russia-china-satellites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国太空部队透露，美国即将部署一种新型地基干扰器，旨在阻止中国或俄罗斯卫星在冲突期间传输有关美军的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/us-space-force-prepares-jammers-to-blunt-russia-china-satellites</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度首家独角兽回国后瞄准 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/india-s-first-unicorn-sets-sights-on-ipo-after-returning-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[移动广告公司 InMobi Pte 计划于明年下半年在印度上市，希望利用世界第五大经济体蓬勃发展的股票市场获利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/india-s-first-unicorn-sets-sights-on-ipo-after-returning-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 09:29:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威银行报告流动性运营出现技术问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/norges-bank-reports-technical-problem-with-liquidity-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球大范围计算机故障影响航空公司、银行和伦敦证券交易所，挪威央行在线系统出现问题，因此央行将不得不于周五通过电子邮件和电话进行银行系统流动性拍卖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/norges-bank-reports-technical-problem-with-liquidity-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 09:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿布扎比马斯达尔计划在 10 亿美元交易后发行更多绿色债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/abu-dhabi-s-masdar-plans-more-green-bonds-after-1-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比的主要可再生能源公司马斯达尔计划在未来几年每年发行绿色债券，为其全球扩张提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/abu-dhabi-s-masdar-plans-more-green-bonds-after-1-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联航、达美航空停止服务，全球航班停飞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-aviation-grinds-to-halt-as-united-delta-stop-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正当全球最繁忙的暑假季节到来之际，大规模的计算机故障导致飞机停飞，机场陷入混乱，世界各地的航空公司经历了前所未有的中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-aviation-grinds-to-halt-as-united-delta-stop-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
